title: SPY SNOW 2014: DANNY LARSEN MARSHALL
description:
As snowboarding's resident black metal powerhouse, Danny Larsen casts a huge shadow over over Europe's version of the Great White North. Danny is one of the most imaginative snowboarders to grace the sport, drawing creative lines in both his snowboarding and artwork, which he lent to the popular Marshall goggle. 

Shop the SPY + Danny Larsen Marshall at http://www.spyoptic.com/store/goggles...
